“But first,” Cody said, “a few preparations.” He reached out and pulled on the door to his left, which closed with a
satisfying thud. Startled, Lulu danced behind Cody and bared her teeth. “Lulu, you know how doors work,” Cody said. Lulu
looked up quizzically, then back at the door, and showed her teeth again. “Never mind,” Cody said,  sighing.
